{"tid":1175542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 世衞首次將「過勞」列為疾病","createTime":"2019-05-28T15:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T10:34:28.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3de50a7aa5d5cfd93245a81b061edcc3f98b27d3","tid":1175542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:22:59.000Z","msg":"在瑞士日內瓦舉行的第72屆世界衞生大會閉幕，首次將「過勞」列為疾病。<br />\n<br />\n世界衞生組織將「過勞」界定為長期無法應付工作壓力導致的症候群，會有三大症狀，包括是感到力量虛耗或筋疲力盡，其後是對工作環境產生抽離，或有負面或不信任感覺，以及專業效率降低。症狀只限於工作環境，而不可應用在其他生活情況。<br />\n<br />\n世衞將「過勞」納入最新通過的《國際疾病分類》第11次修訂版，將於2022年生效。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/world/5ced3c29e60383046286d4a5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Fworld%2F5ced3c29e60383046286d4a5%2F&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2DC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=2d858c90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/world/5ced3c29e60383046286d4a5/</a>"},{"pid":"8da54a0e6e26360b6426a0628765b5f0d4a305b5","tid":1175542,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a84f0a9254ce45313dbebe5cc786b2555b4d6950","tid":1175542,"uid":86509,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:24:47.000Z","msg":"咁醫生可以開醫生紙請病假？"},{"pid":"eda418e878cee0821eaacdca28ad06529835ddcb","tid":1175542,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:26:01.000Z","msg":"諗起班audit狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48c0509fa69b97f4c93c41afb895ce3f434337a","tid":1175542,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:38:37.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意咪唔撚好做 俾你班友高人工都係hea 架啦 你見啲扮工po 就知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗對你班友咁好 俾屎你食就啱"},{"pid":"60f664d109530b5dfbbdabe89115b822372ba360","tid":1175542,"uid":75625,"like